# AWS Standards

Follow the canonical standard: **`.ai/standards/aws-infrastructure.md`**

Key rules:
- Infrastructure as Code — no console-only changes
- Least-privilege IAM
- Secrets in Parameter Store / credentials — never in repo
- Every deployment plan includes rollback steps

